Heather May Metcalfe1

F, #357172, b. 1 May 1965

Last Edited=14 May 2009

Heather May Metcalfe was born on 1 May 1965.1 She is the daughter of David William Metcalfe and Eleanor Constance Leslie-Melville.2 She married Roy Allen Lamont on 27 August 1994.1

From 27 August 1994, her married name became Lamont. She lived in 2003 at 7283 Bell McKinnon Road, Duncan, British Columbia, Canada .1
